# Cloudflare Pages redirects (Netlify-style).
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Legacy Squarespace URLs (/news/...) that Google still has on its radar.
# 301 each one to the closest equivalent on the current Jekyll site so the
# old SC "Not found (404)" report (which failed validation twice) clears
# on Google's next re-crawl. Order matters — specific paths first, then
# the /news/* catch-all.

/news/2019/7/16/is-social-media-necessary-for-my-business    /blog/is-social-media-necessary             301
/news/2019/8/18/perceived-value-and-the-art-of-sales         /blog/perceived-value-and-the-art-of-sales  301
/news/tag/*                                                  /blog                                       301
/news/*                                                      /blog                                       301
/new-page                                                    /                                           301
